Use Case UC3: View Trips

Primary Actor:
Client
Secondary Actor:
Booking System
 
Stakeholders and Interests:

●	Client(s): wants to be able to enter their information and view all their current and past trips
●	Railway Company: desires to provide a booking service to their clients, allowing reliable trip bookings using client's details.


Preconditions:
●   The client is on the main menu of the system and is able to enter their information

Postconditions:
●	 The system displays all of the client's past and current trips
 
Main Success Scenario:
1.        The user selects the option to view past and current trips
2.        The user enters their last name.
3.        The user enters their id.
4.        The user receives all the information kept by the system regarding their past and current trips
